<br>
::Sartha skinned the great animal and removed the head. She cleaned and rolled the gorgeous skin that she would hang respectfully. She cut a piece of meat and raised it to the air::<br>
<br>
&quot;I thank you, Goddess Artemis, for you generosity and kindness. May you always live prominently in the hearts of the Amazons, and blessings to you.&quot;<br>
<br>
::She lowered the meat and ate it carefully. She then put the rest of the animal on a stake and roasted it over a fire she had made. Tonight was a good night...:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/usheyala.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sheyala</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 166<br> <font color=#993300>(6/13/01 9:05:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=214.topic&index=30>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://geocities.com/Tokyo/Pagoda/8446/m-shead.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Hunt</span><hr size=1> ::Shey threw the dagger but it skimmed completely to the side as a large creature landed behind her.  She spun to meet it realizing this is her opponent.  The couger glared at her, its teeth outstretched in challenge.  Shey also realized that she was trapped between the cliff and the predator, just like the fox.  She backed up and the cougar pounced.  Shey swiftly stepped aside and the cougar pounced on top of the white fox who died from the pressure of the cat on it's ribs.  The cougar ignored it and sat back on it's haunches as Shey drew her sword. It refused to attack.::<br>
<br>
&quot;But why don't you...&quot;<br>
<br>
::Shey stopped in sudden understanding.  This was to be a match of equality.  She dropped her sword into it's scabbard and set it aside.  Slowly she shifted into the same type of cougar, only black instead.  She narrowed her eyes and pounced, bringing the other cat to the ground.  After several hours of attack, they both stood face to face, but the brown cougar dropped from exhaustion and shey ended it's honorable life with a snap of her jaws.  Slowly she shifted back and looked up to the heavens.::<br>
<br>
&quot;thank you Artemis for this bountiful hunt, may you always live in the hearts and homes of the amazons.&quot;<br>
<br>
::Shey stalked over and picked up the white fox as well laying it beside the magnificant cat for skinning and drying:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessage?topicID=228.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessage?topicID=226.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=214.topic&index=30><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.emailToFriend?topicID=214.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.threadControl?topicID=214.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=214.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=214.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsuniteamazonsunitescrollboard">Amazons Unite Scroll Board<option value="a